pictures.description: Orange wildflowers blooming among greenery with a backdrop of textured rock formations.
A solitary purple flower basking in the sunlight with a lens flare effect, set against a backdrop of a large rock and shrubs, all resting on a dry, pebbly ground.

A close-up image of coarse, sandy soil with a few large rocks and colorful wildflowers, including yellow poppies and purple blooms, under bright sunlight with blurred natural vegetation in the background.
A close-up of a small purple flower with delicate petals and prominent stamens, growing in gritty soil with a soft-focused background.
pictures.caption: Mastodon Peak in Joshua Tree National Park
